{"tid":126692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被問fb批評法官事件 高志森衝住走人 連講三次：我冇comment","createTime":"2017-02-19T14:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T03:49:29.000Z","uid":1886,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2078c0d9a65e07203f3f367aa435835dc0b52eef","tid":126692,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"被問fb批評法官事件 高志森衝住走人 連講三次：我冇comment<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170219/56325277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170219%2F56325277&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a60b215f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170219%2F56325277&h=907a3e43\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170219/56325277</a><br />\n<br />\n七警傷人案自七名警員被判罪成，高志森連日來喺社交平台facebook都有高度批評，就連法官都唔放過，更指「香港法律那一條是『不可以批評法官』的？」、「公道判案的是法官，偏頗判案的是狗官，對號入座吧。」今日高志森喺灣仔出席分享會，匆匆來又匆匆去，喺活動最遲嚟到嘅嘉賓，事後又話要趕住去做嘢，急急腳冇接受訪問就要走，仲衝住去搭lift。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170219/large/1487494671_9de5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170219%2Flarge%2F1487494671_9de5.jpg&h=b1bfb631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲好似好忙咁睇電話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170219/large/1487494674_d00d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170219%2Flarge%2F1487494674_d00d.jpg&h=0e0c4452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入到lift焗住接受訪問<br />\n<br />\n對於各界對事件批評，司法機構回應高度關注近日有人喺社交媒體發表對個別法官評論，已轉介律政司跟進，高志森喺lift中被問及呢件事，佢連續兩次話：「我冇comment。」問到佢其facebook曾講過：「公道判案的是法官，偏頗判案的是狗官，對號入座吧。」嘅post刪除咗，係咪因怕會有影響？高志森話：「對唔住，呢個問題我冇comment。」噚日有撐警員嘅遊行，問到高志森點解唔出席支持，佢都只係答：「我冇comment。」"},{"pid":"78347a0a3285b28c053f6988485e6824cd83c220","tid":126692,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />柒到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e87f0c3ba20f7e00306904b6cb7bd5c8d09815","tid":126692,"uid":5463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懦撚到佢"},{"pid":"205ef7a1b437c15b3aed30cfd119156b2cd768b8","tid":126692,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:18:24.000Z","msg":"咁快潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882cbb9f965ba992033e08a878e414223edc79b6","tid":126692,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631db6ef3a4a2dd0b7464b5b90b3f0e9e803950d","tid":126692,"uid":65825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:25:20.000Z","msg":"好撚肉鳩酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadc0e1fe5200bcfb1d1965a370f10c4d49f2706","tid":126692,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fcd4a9b547842b41827174ed1229708e344c61","tid":126692,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/3